#G-Less
##Simple graphical less replacement, *nothing more, nothing less*

This programm shows the content of a single text file, in the spirit of less, but with syntax highlighting, line numbering and graphical user interaction.

##Dependencies

* cmake
* vala
* gtk3
* gtksourceview

##Build

Once you cloned the repository and `cd` into the cloned directory:

```shell
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
```

*Extra:* `make install` for, you know, install it ;)



